  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_1_2",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "身前是从液态甲烷般的幽暗中升起的未知存在。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_1_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_1_3",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "她的双眸如星辰般闪烁，",
    "next": "dream_prologue_1_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_1_4",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "却透露着千年的疲惫。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_1_5"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_1_5",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "在这个超越时空的维度里，她是唯一的守望者。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_1_2_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_1_2_1",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "也是最后的希望。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_2_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_2_1",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "她对峙的，或许是这实体本身，",
    "next": "dream_prologue_2_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_2_2",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "或许是它折射出的、超越日常维度的认知褶皱——",
    "next": "dream_prologue_2_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_2_3",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "那些视网膜无法解析的现实裂缝。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_2_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_2_4",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "每一次呼吸，都是对混沌的抗争。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_2_5"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_2_5",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "每一次心跳，都在为即将到来的命运做准备。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_1",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "认知时间以千年为刻度流淌，",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_2",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "身旁过客如现实碎片般更迭。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_3",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "但当圈境的符文潮汐退去，",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_4",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "当蚀影体的低语沉入维度夹缝，",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_5"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_5",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "唯有她的身影仍在原地。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_2_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_2_1",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "孤独，是万象行者永恒的宿命。",
    "next": "dream_prologue_3_2_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "dream_prologue_3_2_2",
    "type": "narration",
    "background": "game/videos/backgrounds/dream_prologue.mp4",
    "speaker": "旁白",
    "text": "直到那个少年的出现……",
    "next": "male_intro_1_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_1_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "转校第一天，第十二次在同一个校园里迷路……",
    "next": "male_intro_1_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_1_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "果然，我的方向感已经烂到超越了人类的极限。",
    "next": "male_intro_1_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_1_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "但又不是普通的迷路……",
    "next": "male_intro_1_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_1_4",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "更像是这个空间本身在对我撒谎。",
    "next": "male_intro_2_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_2_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "比如现在，教学楼的轮廓线在轻微地\"融化\"，",
    "next": "male_intro_2_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_2_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "就像夏日柏油路上的热浪，",
    "next": "male_intro_2_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_2_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/male_intro.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "可今天明明是个秋高气爽的日子。",
    "next": "male_intro_3_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "祖父常说，我们家的人能看到\"世界的另一面\"。",
    "next": "male_intro_3_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "以前我只当是故事，",
    "next": "male_intro_3_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "但自从他把那本《星图异闻录》留给我之后，",
    "next": "male_intro_3_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_3_4",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "这种\"异常\"就越来越频繁了……",
    "next": "male_intro_4_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_4_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "嗯？那是……在做什么？",
    "next": "male_intro_4_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_4_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "那个女生……",
    "next": "male_intro_4_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_4_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "她在对着空气说话？",
    "next": "male_intro_4_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "male_intro_4_4",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "陈星",
    "text": "还是在念什么咒语？",
    "next": "heroine_protocol_1_1"
  },
  {
    "id": "heroine_protocol_1_1",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "魏娇娇",
    "text": "初始化协议……\"卡珊德拉\"上线。",
    "next": "heroine_protocol_1_2"
  },
  {
    "id": "heroine_protocol_1_2",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "魏娇娇",
    "text": "开始同步本地现实参数……",
    "next": "heroine_protocol_1_3"
  },
  {
    "id": "heroine_protocol_1_3",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "魏娇娇",
    "text": "(设备哔声)",
    "next": "heroine_protocol_1_4"
  },
  {
    "id": "heroine_protocol_1_4",
    "type": "dialogue",
    "background": "game/videos/cutscenes/opening.mp4",
    "speaker": "魏娇娇",
    "text": "报告总部，\"青藤高中\"象限，",
